Package com.epoch.qBank

Classes for topics, question sets, and questions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaptionsQDatum
    Stores captions of rows or columns in table questions of columns in orbital energy diagram questions.
    EDiagramQDatum
    Stores pulldown menu options and y-axis scale parameters in energy diagram questions.
    Figure
    Refers to a single figure (structure, reaction or image) used by a question.
    QDatum
    Data used by a question that is not associated with any one evaluator.
    QSetDescr
    The descriptive attributes of a question set; for display and editing.
    Question
    An ACE question, formerly called a problem.
    TextChapters
    Singleton class that stores the names of textbook chapters.
    Topic
    Holds topic information while viewing/editing/adding topic.
